summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from J. B. Sanford and Eva A. Sanford, his wife, and Christmas G. Evans and Bertha Evans, his wife, all of Helena Montana, to the City of Seattle dated the 28th day of June, 1907 to Lots five (5), six (6) and nine (9) Block eight (8), Lot five (5) Block nine (9), Lots one (1), two (2), five (5), six (6), and seven (7) Block ten (10) and Lots one (1), two (2), four (4), five (5) and six (6) Block eleven (11) all of Craven's Division of Green Lake Addition to the City of Seattle.
